      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768490391854,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Also, each step’s state is stored so it can resume from\nwhere it left off. Background processes can run for a long\ntime without us having to worry about serverless timeouts",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "U2USnM5XC0p7_wAW44UTQ",
      "originalText": "Also, each step’s state is stored so it can resume from where it left off. Background processes can run for a long time without us having to worry about serverless timeouts",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
