      "updated": 1768490513404,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. We've already tested out code with \"modal run main.py\"\n2. Run \"modal deploy main.py\"\n3. The built container is deployed and end endpoints exposed\n4. In the terminal we can see the URL for hitting the endpoints",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. We've already tested out code with \"modal run main.py\"\n2. Run \"modal deploy main.py\"\n3. The built container is deployed and end endpoints exposed\n4. In the terminal we can see the URL for hitting the endpoints",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
