    {
      "id": "EwRwFMRcwhP1tldWGwM_E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7472.596330531673,
      "y": 132.21356923535592,
      "width": 424.66532216757173,
      "height": 270.0517531569958,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bYQ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1286827078,
      "version": 1157,
      "versionNonce": 504768691,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768489999154,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. App checks that the scene description isn't empty\n\n2. Supabase Edge Function Call (supabase.functions.invoke(\"scenario-\ngenerate\")\n\n** Inside edge function **\n3. Verifies the user has a valid Supabase Auth token. Checks the\nprofiles table to ensure the user is Premium.\n\n4. It constructs a prompt for google/gemini-3-flash-preview via\nOpenRouter and does fetch (api call)\n\n5. Parses answer and returns it to client\n\n** Back in the client **\n6. Persist the new scenario to local storage\n\n7. Automatically open intro screen for new scenario",
      "fontSize": 12.002300140310926,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. App checks that the scene description isn't empty\n\n2. Supabase Edge Function Call (supabase.functions.invoke(\"scenario-generate\")\n\n** Inside edge function **\n3. Verifies the user has a valid Supabase Auth token. Checks the profiles table to ensure the user is Premium.\n\n4. It constructs a prompt for google/gemini-3-flash-preview via OpenRouter and does fetch (api call)\n\n5. Parses answer and returns it to client\n\n** Back in the client **\n6. Persist the new scenario to local storage\n\n7. Automatically open intro screen for new scenario",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
