      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768489999155,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Uses audio (if present) to get a transcript.\n\nGenerate an AI response with OpenRouter\nbased on the conversation history + scenario\ncontext.\n\nReturn a JSON object containing:\n- userTranscript (what the user said, if audio\nwas used).\n- text / hanzi / pinyin / english (the AI's\nresponse).\n- conversationComplete flag (if the goal is\nmet).",
      "fontSize": 12.002300140310926,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Uses audio (if present) to get a transcript.\n\nGenerate an AI response with OpenRouter based on the conversation history + scenario context.\n\nReturn a JSON object containing:\n- userTranscript (what the user said, if audio was used).\n- text / hanzi / pinyin / english (the AI's response).\n- conversationComplete flag (if the goal is met).",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
